{"tid":576344,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺以為痴埋中國會有游水既人好短視","createTime":"2018-02-28T22:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T12:30:15.000Z","uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"424ee8ce3afa6d44c57f3583e95c25127e425a03","tid":576344,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T22:25:55.000Z","msg":"先唔理香港建制定反對<br />\n<br />\n根本中國係唔想理香港人<br />\n你香港人仲要痴埋上去<br />\n人地只會討厭你<br />\n<br />\n對香港人最好選擇只有一個<br />\n<br />\n就係 香港要不同於中國<br />\n<br />\n香港唔能夠永遠睇中國做大佬，幾時先有意識小小仲係到亞爺亞爺 仲親過你落街幫你睇門口個保安？<br />\n<br />\n叫香港派錢不如叫中國派錢<br />\n<br />\n叫香港投資落內地不如投資落本地<br />\n<br />\n就算投資一百億一千億落去香港搞屎搞棍，都仲係叫投本地，但你一投去中國，就理虧喇。"},{"pid":"a164c099a5fed2dae88e15af2aa3f3607d12d72f","tid":576344,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T22:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3559e5e5b576cfaa17bac1a7541f5f1c51029c9","tid":576344,"uid":160688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"油水"},{"pid":"f3a06127cb74a317afbc6020935565db010aa388","tid":576344,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"菲比斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ed32f1d2baba3dde1bc25ab0e7a4fd3734409d","tid":576344,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:15:10.000Z","msg":"游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16817cd5b23c6567dbd4326564dcceb287fcbb41","tid":576344,"uid":64948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T12:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔洗痴埋去我都有游水喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}